<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Posta — Cast Iron Post Box Hire, Ireland</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Premium cast iron post box hire for Irish weddings. Delivered to your venue, collected the morning after.">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/public/home.css">
</head>
<body>

  <header class="nav" id="nav" role="banner">
    <a href="/" class="nav-wordmark">Posta</a>
    <a href="/enquiry" class="nav-cta btn btn-outline-accent">Enquire</a>
  </header>

  <main id="main-content">

    <div class="sections-wrapper">

    <section class="grid-container grid-1" aria-labelledby="title">

      <div class="card-outer fade-slow">
        <div class="card card-1">
          <p class="hero-kicker">Wedding &ensp;&middot;&ensp; Rentals</p>
          <h1 class="hero-title" id="title">
            The Post Box<br>
            To<br>
            Remember
          </h1>
          <p class="hero-desc">
            Collect your cards with a classic, beautiful post box for your wedding day. Quirky with a vintage charm. 
            Delivered to your venue and collected the next day.
          </p>
          <a href="/products" class="hero-link">
            View the collection
            <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-outer card-outer-2 fade-fast">
        <img src="/images/public/posta-square-6.png" alt="Cast iron post box" loading="eager" fetchpriority="high">
        <div class="card card-2"></div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <section class="grid-container grid-2" aria-label="What we offer">

      <div class="card-outer card-outer-3 reveal-left">
        <img src="/images/public/posta-night-land.png" alt="" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="card card-3">
          <span class="card-num">01</span>
          <h2 class="card-title">The Collection</h2>
          <p class="card-desc">Cast iron post boxes available to hire. Each piece unique.</p>
          <a href="/products" class="card-link btn btn-text-light">
            Browse all pieces
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-outer card-outer-4 reveal-right">
        <div class="card card-4">
          <div>
            <span class="card-num">02</span>
            <h2 class="card-title">Availability</h2>
            <p class="card-desc">Check which pieces are free for your date.</p>
            <div class="avail-mock" aria-hidden="true">
              <label class="avail-mock-label">Your wedding date</label>
              <input class="avail-mock-field" type="date" tabindex="-1">
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="/availability" class="card-link btn btn-text-dark">
            Check availability
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-outer card-outer-5 reveal-right">
        <div class="card card-5">
          <div>
            <span class="card-num">03</span>
            <h2 class="card-title">Enquire</h2>
            <p class="card-desc">Tell us your date and venue. We reply within 24 hours.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/enquiry" class="card-link btn btn-text-light">
            Make an enquiry
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <section class="grid-container grid-3">

      <div class="card-outer reveal-left">
        <div class="card card-6">
          <div>
            <h2 class="card-title-sm">Delivery</h2>
            <p class="card-desc">Nationwide. We deliver and collect — you don't lift a thing.</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/delivery" class="card-link btn btn-text-dark">
            View delivery areas
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-outer reveal-bottom">
        <div class="card card-7">
          <div>
            <h2 class="card-title-sm">Just Ask</h2>
            <p class="card-desc">Not sure, just get in touch. Need more info on delivery, price, dates or anything else?</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/about" class="card-link btn btn-text-dark">
            Contact us
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-outer reveal-right">
        <div class="card card-8">
          <div>
            <h2 class="card-title-sm">Personal Touch</h2>
            <p class="card-desc">Create you own card for the font with anything you wish or we can print something for you</p>
          </div>
          <a href="/custom-cards" class="card-link btn btn-text-dark">
            View custom cards
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <section class="grid-container grid-4" aria-label="The object">

      <div class="card-outer card-outer-9 reveal-left">
        <img src="/images/public/posta-lock.jpeg" alt="" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="card card-9"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-outer card-outer-10 reveal-left">
        <img src="/images/public/manor%20table.png" alt="" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="card card-10"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="card-outer card-outer-11 reveal-right">
        <img src="/images/public/posta-square-6.png" alt="" loading="lazy" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="card card-11"></div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <section class="grid-container grid-5">
      <div class="card-outer reveal-fade">
      <div class="card card-12">
        <div class="info-blob" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <div class="info-body">
          <h3 class="info-heading">What We Offer</h3>
          <p>Posta hires original antique cast iron post boxes for wedding days across Ireland. Each piece is lockable and secure, keeping cards safe throughout your day. They bring real weight and character to any table setting — and because guests post independently, there is no need for anyone to manage card collection on the day itself.</p>
          <h3 class="info-heading">How It Works</h3>
          <p>Check availability for your date and make an enquiry with your venue details. We offer full delivery and collection to your venue, or self-collection if you prefer. Delivery is free to venues in Wicklow, Kildare, Meath, and Louth — all other locations quoted on enquiry. If nothing is showing for your date, get in touch anyway — we may be able to source a piece.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    </div>

  </main>

  <footer class="footer" role="contentinfo">
    <div class="footer-grid">
      <div class="footer-col">
        <a href="/" class="footer-brand">Posta</a>
        <p class="footer-tagline">{{ companySettings.tagline if companySettings and companySettings.tagline else 'Cast iron post box hire for Irish weddings.' }}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <span class="footer-col-label">Explore</span>
        <ul class="footer-links" role="list">
          <li><a href="/products">Collection</a></li>
          <li><a href="/availability">Availability</a></li>
          <li><a href="/delivery">Delivery</a></li>
          <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
          <li><a href="/enquiry">Enquire</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <span class="footer-col-label">Contact</span>
        <ul class="footer-links" role="list">
          {% if companySettings and companySettings.contactPhone %}
            <li><a href="tel:{{ companySettings.contactPhone }}">{{ companySettings.contactPhone }}</a></li>
          {% endif %}
          {% if companySettings and companySettings.contactEmail %}
            <li><a href="mailto:{{ companySettings.contactEmail }}">{{ companySettings.contactEmail }}</a></li>
          {% endif %}
          <li><a href="/legal">Terms &amp; Conditions</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-base">
      <span>&copy; {{ currentYear }} {{ companySettings.companyName if companySettings and companySettings.companyName else 'Posta' }}. All rights reserved.</span>
      <a href="/legal">Terms &amp; Conditions</a>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <script src="/js/public/reveal.js" defer></script>
  <script src="/js/public/home.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>
